              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="bedrooms__form-function form-function">
            <div class="form-function__header">
              <h2 class="form-function__title">Form and function</h2>
              <p class="form-function__desc">
                A made to measure wardrobe is a practical solution for your
                home, making use of every inch of space and creating a seamless
                interior finish to your bedroom.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="form-function__body">
              <div
