                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="form-function__footer">
                <div class="form-function__footer-image">
                  <img src="img/bed-fot.jpg" alt="" />
                </div>
                <div class="form-function__footer-text-block">
                  <div class="form-function__footer-caption">
                    Small spaces demand efficient storage solutions too
